creator: D & D Marketing
descriptionHtml: The target audience for this app are the visitors and permanent residents that are located in Lake Havasu City, Arizona. The main purpose of this app is to provide assistance on accommodations, nearby businesses and other attractions in Lake Havasu City. It is a general information guide for travel. The app includes features such as a district map, business directory, attractions, weather, accomodations and coupons / offers from local businesses.
descriptionShort: Travel Guide for Lake Havasu City, Arizona
